articles.title: Rahul Gandhi gets new passport, set to travel to US on Monday - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Rahul Gandhi is likely to address Indian Americans and interact with Wall Street executives and university students during his week-long tour of the USA. | Latest News India
articles.content:
Congress leader Rahul Gandhi received a new ordinary passport on Sunday, two days after a Delhi court gave its clearance, sources said.
